              <h1 class="visually-hidden">The Québec Ombudsman</h1>
            <a id="main-content" tabindex="-1"></a>
              
                  <div id="highlighted">  <div class="region region-highlighted">
      <div class="slider">
    <div class="before"></div>
  	<ul>
  		  		    <li>
  		    	<img src="https://protecteurducitoyen.qc.ca/sites/default/files/images/slider/slider1_4.jpg" alt="Administration" title="Administration" width="1400" height="540">
  		    	<div class="caption">
	  		    	<div class="wrapper">
	  		    		<div class="caption-content">
	  		    			<h2>Problem with an institution within the <strong>health and social services network</strong>?</h2>

<p>The <strong>Québec Ombudsman</strong> can help you. As a second instance.</p>

<p><a class="white-button" href="/en/health-and-social-services">For more information <span class="visuallyhidden">about the health and social services network</span></a></p>

	  		    		</div>
	  		    	</div>
  		    	</div>
  		    </li>
  		  		    <li>
  		    	<img src="https://protecteurducitoyen.qc.ca/sites/default/files/images/slider/slider2_4.jpg" alt="Santé" title="Santé" width="1400" height="540">
  		    	<div class="caption">
	  		    	<div class="wrapper">
	  		    		<div class="caption-content">
	  		    			<h2>Problem with a Government of Québec <strong>department</strong> or <strong>agency</strong>?</h2>

<p>The <strong>Québec Ombudsman</strong> can help you.</p>

<p><a class="white-button" href="/en/make-a-complaint/how-to-make-a-complaint">For more information <span class="visuallyhidden">on how to make a complaint</span></a></p>

	  		    		</div>
	  		    	</div>
  		    	</div>
  		    </li>
  		  		    <li>
  		    	<img src="https://protecteurducitoyen.qc.ca/sites/default/files/images/slider/slider3_4.jpg" alt="Recours" title="Recours" width="1400" height="540">
  		    	<div class="caption">
	  		    	<div class="wrapper">
	  		    		<div class="caption-content">
	  		    			<h2><strong>Independent</strong>, <strong>simple</strong> and <strong>free</strong> <strong>recourse</strong></h2>

<p>The <b>Québec Ombudsman</b> ensures that your <strong>rights are upheld</strong> in your dealings with public services.</p>

<p><a class="white-button" href="/en/about-us/role-and-mandates">For more information <span class="visuallyhidden">about the Québec Ombudsman's roles and mandates</span></a></p>

	  		    		</div>
	  		    	</div>
  		    	</div>
  		    </li>
  		  	</ul>
  	<div class="slider-controls" aria-hidden="true">
  		<div class="wrapper">
