<h2 class="date">Tell us what you think of the Québec Ombudsman’s website!</h2>
<p>How would you rate your browsing experience? How can we optimize the quality of our online services?</p>
<p>Help us better meet your needs <strong>by taking part in a brief survey</strong> containing eight questions that only take a few minutes to answer. </p>
<ul><li><a href="http://bit.ly/webSurv" target="_blank" title="This link will open in a new window">Participate</a></li>
</ul></div>
